@startuml

title 错误到退出码状态图

[*] --> Running

Running --> Success : no exception
Success --> Exit0 : return 0

Running --> ConfigError : ConfigError
ConfigError --> Exit10 : exit_code=10

Running --> DownloadError : DownloadError
DownloadError --> Exit20 : exit_code=20

Running --> SignatureVerifyError : SignatureVerifyError
SignatureVerifyError --> Exit40 : exit_code=40

Running --> InstallError : InstallError
InstallError --> Exit50 : exit_code=50

Running --> CleanupError : CleanupError
CleanupError --> Exit60 : exit_code=60

Running --> UnknownException : non-InstallerError
UnknownException --> Exit1 : main() fallback

@enduml
